{
  "stem": "16571.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 380.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no impression.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were holding on to-- virtually to each other's hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were frightened of the shadows, even in England.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we arrived in England, we sort of began to associate, like, with friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at first when we arrived in the hostels, they used to put food on the table.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to fill our pockets up with white bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We haven't seen white bread for years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to behave like animals, I realize now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to-- we never fought or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was that-- we were still under the shadow of what we went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were still frightened there won't be any tomorrow or later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm ashamed to say we were like animals in some way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Gradually, you realize that you don't have to do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You-- it-- it's-- the food is there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's no shortage, and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we gradually sort of eased off from filling our pockets up with bread or whatever was going.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was in this hostel, as I said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "About six weeks, I was in a hostel in Southampton.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we were taken to Scotland, traveled hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It sounded-- for, like, 15 hours, them days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'm going--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got on the train in Southampton to London.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We changed in London.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We traveled a whole night to Glasgow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then another local train-- it seemed like take for ages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We arrived in this hostel, which was called-- and Cardross was the village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Dulles ?] House was-- the place was called [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Dulles ?] House.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was already a group of boys and girls who came from Theresienstadt to Windermere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from Windermere, they closed up that place.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
